memberdef.name: URHO3D_MAKE_MEMBER_ATTRIBUTE_ACCESSOR
memberdef.initializer: Urho3D::MakeVariantAttributeAccessor<ClassName>( \ [](const ClassName& self, Urho3D::Variant& value) { value = self.variable; }, \ [](ClassName& self, const Urho3D::Variant& value) { self.variable = value.Get<typeName>(); })

memberdef.name: URHO3D_MAKE_MEMBER_ATTRIBUTE_ACCESSOR_EX
memberdef.initializer: Urho3D::MakeVariantAttributeAccessor<ClassName>( \ [](const ClassName& self, Urho3D::Variant& value) { value = self.variable; }, \ [](ClassName& self, const Urho3D::Variant& value) { self.variable = value.Get<typeName>(); self.postSetCallback(); })

briefdescription.para: Make member attribute accessor with custom post-set callback.

memberdef.name: URHO3D_MAKE_GET_SET_ATTRIBUTE_ACCESSOR
memberdef.initializer: Urho3D::MakeVariantAttributeAccessor<ClassName>( \ [](const ClassName& self, Urho3D::Variant& value) { value = self.getFunction(); }, \ [](ClassName& self, const Urho3D::Variant& value) { self.setFunction(value.Get<typeName>()); })

memberdef.name: URHO3D_MAKE_MEMBER_ENUM_ATTRIBUTE_ACCESSOR
memberdef.initializer: Urho3D::MakeVariantAttributeAccessor<ClassName>( \ [](const ClassName& self, Urho3D::Variant& value) { value = static_cast<int>(self.variable); }, \ [](ClassName& self, const Urho3D::Variant& value) { self.variable = static_cast<decltype(self.variable)>(value.Get<int>()); })

memberdef.name: URHO3D_MAKE_MEMBER_ENUM_ATTRIBUTE_ACCESSOR_EX
memberdef.initializer: Urho3D::MakeVariantAttributeAccessor<ClassName>( \ [](const ClassName& self, Urho3D::Variant& value) { value = static_cast<int>(self.variable); }, \ [](ClassName& self, const Urho3D::Variant& value) { self.variable = static_cast<decltype(self.variable)>(value.Get<int>()); self.postSetCallback(); })
